    • Method Detail

      • registerCommand

        protected boolean registerCommand(String triggerName,
                                  CommandTrigger trigger)
        Description copied from class: AbstractCommandTriggerManager
        Register this command to command map. If the command is already in use by another plugin, the original command will be overriden, and the original command will be recovered when the trigger is un-registered. However, if the trigger's name is already registered and also overriden by another command trigger, this method does nothing and return false.
        Specified by:
        registerCommand in class AbstractCommandTriggerManager
        Parameters:
        triggerName - name of the trigger to register
        trigger - the actual trigger instance
        Returns:
        true if registered; false if the command is already overriden by another command trigger and is also already registered trigger, it will return false.

      • unregisterCommand

        Description copied from class: AbstractCommandTriggerManager
        Unregister this command from command map.
        Specified by:
        unregisterCommand in class AbstractCommandTriggerManager
        Parameters:

        Returns:
